(3) Grant the read privileges on the relational table PREFERENCE in the database csit115 to the second user who has been created in (1). 
The privileges must be granted such that the second user can propagate the same privileges to other roles or users.
*/

GRANT SELECT ON csit115.PREFERENCE TO 'ntt607_2'@'localhost' WITH GRANT OPTION
